To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AccelerationBands _abands;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_abands = ABANDS(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_abands.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "middleband", _abands.MiddleBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "upperband", _abands.UpperBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "lowerband", _abands.LowerBand.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "accelerationbands", _abands.Current.Value);
}
